    question: 'Attentive or Recart for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Attentive when Larger DTC brands with high SMS volume. Choose Recart when Stores focused on cart recovery via mobile channels. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
